      <hedline>
        <hl1>Weird and Scary</hl1>
      </hedline>
      <abstract>
        <p>Albert Lee letter on Ben Ratliff's July 16 article opposes Pat Metheny's comments on Kenny g's overdub on Louis Armstrong track (S)</p>
      </abstract>
    </body.head>
    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>To the Editor:</p>
        <p>I took Pat Metheny's comments on Kenny G's overdub on a Louis Armstrong track more seriously than did Ben Ratliff. It's hazardous for an artist to level such a complaint at a colleague. It angers the great number of fans who support Kenny G. And much more than the negligible performances of Kenny G, the numb receptivity of these fans is, after all, what some of us find so weird and scary.</p>
        <p>ALBERT LEE  Manhattan</p>
      </block>
